summary:
Solution-driven Business Analyst eager to derive and effectively communicate actionable insights from the data. Recognized for being proactive and bringing creative ideas outside of the box, thereby leading teams forward. Excel and enjoy communicating in teams with various backgrounds thanks to the solid international experience and valuable language skills. With my problem-solving abilities, I am aspired to make a positive change in the world towards sustainability.

Fun fact: I am in the top 99,51th percentile in Mathematics Matriculation exam in Ukraine.
